{
  "stem": "23090.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was never the same, I can tell you that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know, maybe-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I just could not think very well anymore at that particular juncture.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it took me a long time to just come around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, to me, it seemed like a long-- I was just having these headaches, and I was moving slowly, and I don't know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It just-- I have to attribute it to that particular time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they assigned me to-- in Kaufbeuren, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they assigned me to a detail up in the-- a kitchen detail.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was 10 of us, 12 of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a kitchen-- a German kitchen a few kilometers from the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This camp was a fairly new camp in Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to go to this camp, to this kitchen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was our job, is to go to this kitchen, peel potatoes, and carrots, and cabbages, and so on and so forth, all day long.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was-- this kitchen was cooking for the German soldiers, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then we would get the potato peelings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they would make, from the potato peelings, we would get the soups and so on for our camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there's a little humor and tragedy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was a part of humor, because they assigned to us a older German soldier from the kaiser.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The man had to be in his, maybe, 70s.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he wore those long bixes, the bixes, the long rifle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, those long, heavy rifle, and he had to wear this long trench, the German coats, with the ammunition, and his canteen, and the rest of the paraphernalia, the rest of the military garb that he had to wear.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
